text:
Natak krna padta tha bhai kyunki mai optionless tha.
Tmhare bulane ke chakkar me TT sikha badminton sikha magar hasana nii sikh paya.

Bhai tmhari smile v canteen ke menu me honi chahiye.

Keep Enjoying!!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Tm wo ho jo hamesa rhythm me rehana chahata hai,
Shayad isliye log tmhe sunana chahate hai,
Aur jo nii sunana chahate wo tmhare sath maggi khate hai!!

Tm wo ho jo samjhane se jyada sunana pasand krta hai ðŸ˜ ,
Tm wo ho jo jazbaati hota to nii magar krne me ghalib ban jaata hai,
Tm wo ho jo masti ke ahosh me dubana chahata hai magar behakana nii chahata,

Tm to shayar ho aakhir kaun tmko itna tadpata hai!!

Bhai yaha pe wahi likha  jo kvi bol nii hai baki to sb yaad hi hai.IT chicken darbar jana hai pulkit ko bata ke nii le jana hai.

Keep Enjoying!!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Tm to padosi the tmhe to pta hona chahiye tha zamane ke baare me,
Magar tm apne kilkariyo me madhosh rehana chahate the!!

Shayad tmhe ganje ka nasha so ke uthane ke baad hota tha,
Isiliye mai v madhoshi ka natak tmhare samane  kr liya krta tha!!

Sath uthate the sath khate the magar sath ro nii paate the kyunki mere pass ansu nii the aur tmhare pass gum nii tha!!

Bhai khush raho abaad rho zindabad rho baaki IT chicken darbar jana hai aur pulkit ko bata ke nii le jana hai.

Keep Enjoying!!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Bhai pehle to tmhe thanks bolunga jo shayad abtk nii bola tmhe!!Aur suno

Bahut hilte the  magar dusaro ko hilane se bachate the tm,
Chappal fek ke marna chahte the  magar aur be bolke mera chappal le jate the tm,
Abe kaise hoga bol ke darate the  magar ye lo chaap lo bolke  khus kr dete the tm,
Mere escape aur IITK ke bich ka connection the tm,
Aur kya bolu bahut maggi khate the tm!!

Keep enjoying !!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Tmne jo socha tha wo hm the nii aur maine jo socha tha tm usse v badhkar the!!

Keep Enjoying!!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Shobhit yaar bhula dena mujhe accha roomie to nii tha aur samajh me ane wala v nii isiliye kuch bolte nii the tm hmko.
Keep smiling!!
author: Krishna Prakash Roy

text:
Bhai tm game km khelate to jyada harami ban paate.Aur upar se tmhara roomie aman waisehi tha jaise mera roomie.Use v apne jaisa bana liye the.Bhand hona v kafi baad me suru kiya tune magar maja aya.

Keep Playing !!
